metadata.name: FM365 #1 Nine Ball
metadata.description:
Flying Mouse 365 (FM365) is a personal art project by award-winning artist, Chow Hon Lam.  The series comprised of Chow creating ‘one design per day’ for an entire year - of which he succesfully completed in 2011.

In celebration of this series, Chow has decided to mint all 365 designs as NFTS :  limiting only ONE edition to each artwork, with a generous reward to all Holders.  The Holder will own the rights of the digital collectible art, and license to use the art in all kinds of personal or commercial usage. To claim the high-resolutions files, email us at reward@flyingmouse365.io.
